ical observations performed in the present society. Finally, it is evaluated how adequate is Reinhart Kosellecks theory of historical times to the temporal complexity of the modern society.", "Data de Liberação": "2019-02-08", "Data de Publicação": "2017-04-05", "url": "http://www.teses.usp.br/teses/disponiveis/2/2139/tde-13012017-163206/pt-br.php"}
